_:N195fdd9396534ea984fd03ea5f62a42b <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Douglas Alexander was appointed Secretary of State for Scotland on 5 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>He previously Minister of State at the Department for Business and Trade between 6 July 2024 and 5 September 2025, and Minister of State in the Cabinet Office between 10 February 2025 and 5 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>He was elected as the MP for Lothian East in July 2024.</p>\n" .
